      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for its next adventure! I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home where it\u2019ll be appreciated as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
