    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving masterpiece. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, it delivers linear power through a 6-speed manual gearbox and a M-Variable differential lock. The chassis has been addressed with essential subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh to ensure long-term reliability. Equipped with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, the handling remains sharp and communicative. While the finish shows minor road wear, the drivetrain is dialed-in for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
