      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, honest character marks expected from careful road use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with supple upholstery, crisp instrumentation, and all convenience features functioning exactly as intended. Mechanically, it has been pampered with a consistent service schedule; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it is road-ready from day one. Sold with a complete set of floor mats and a detailed service history, this car offers a premium driving experience for the discerning owner who values quality and reliability.",
